    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>风格化的视觉效果和配乐：</strong> 体验制作精美的比例模型风格视觉效果和轻松、大气的配乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[引人入胜的战斗和挑战：</strong> 与来势汹汹的敌人作战，克服危险的障碍，逃离致命的陷阱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121850/extras/1a5e06d523ba809b72fdb91223f0106d.poster.avif?t=1764338052\" width=624 height=386 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121850/extras/1a5e06d523ba809b72fdb91223f0106d.webm?t=1764338052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121850/extras/1a5e06d523ba809b72fdb91223f0106d.mp4?t=1764338052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>错综复杂的谜题：</strong> 解决具有挑战性的谜题，考验您的技能和战略思维。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神秘环境</strong>： 探索充满秘密通道和禁区的环境，为您的任务增添深度和趣味性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多用途工具：</strong> 利用各种工具，包括分散注意力、伪装、藏身点、陷阱、传送门和步枪来智取敌人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121850/extras/f0296f27163b542a338247ebf44d3e3f.poster.avif?t=1764338052\" width=624 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121850/extras/f0296f27163b542a338247ebf44d3e3f.webm?t=1764338052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121850/extras/f0296f27163b542a338247ebf44d3e3f.mp4?t=1764338052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样化的敌人类型：</strong> 面对具有独特致命行为的敌人类型。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收藏品和定制：</strong> 收集遗物并解锁乌希兰特的新服装，为您的游戏增添一层个性化色彩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多种方法：</strong> 完成每个关卡的方法多种多样，可以选择沉默隐蔽，也可以选择强硬攻击。目标是收集难以捉摸的背包或在特定的移动次数内完成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121850/extras/b14dbd4b4c7b720a96bfd78249b0eb25.poster.avif?t=1764338052\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121850/extras/b14dbd4b4c7b720a96bfd78249b0eb25.webm?t=1764338052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121850/extras/b14dbd4b4c7b720a96bfd78249b0eb25.mp4?t=1764338052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富的关卡：</strong> 50 多个关卡以多种方式尝试游戏的机制，挑战您对规则的理解和运用。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>角色故事：</strong> 通过乌希兰特携带的物品了解他的故事，为您的旅程增加叙事深度。</p>",
